&gt;&gt; /Daniel
&gt;&gt; On 2025-07-02 17:26, Alex Russell wrote:
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Per conversation at today's API OWNERS, LGTM1 contingent on there being a
&gt;&gt; stand-alone explainer and example code. Bonus points for getting motivating
